t\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"ProductCatalogService响应时间从正常约10秒激增至3900万毫秒，延迟倍数高达4000倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"出现大量'Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable'错误，表明底层TiDB数据库区域不可用\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Frontend服务调用ProductCatalogService时响应时间从11秒激增至3900万毫秒，是下游异常的受害者\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Checkout服务调用ProductCatalogService时响应时间从19秒激增至4000万毫秒，同样受下游影响\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 关键发现总结：\n\n1. **根因定位**: ProductCatalogService是问题根源，所有异常都源于它调用TiDB时出现的\"Region is unavailable\"错误。\n\n2. **延迟异常**: 多个服务的响应时间都出现了极端延迟：\n   - ProductCatalogService: 10秒 → 3900万毫秒 (4000倍延迟)\n   - Frontend: 11-15秒 → 3900万毫秒\n   - CheckoutService: 15-19秒 → 4000万毫秒\n\n3. **错误传播路径**: \n   - TiDB数据库区域不可用 → ProductCatalogService异常 → Frontend/CheckoutService异常\n\n4. **影响范围**: 主要影响产品目录查询和下单流程，特别是GetProduct和PlaceOrder操作。\n\n建议下一步进行深度分析，重点关注TiDB数据库的状态和ProductCatalogService与数据库的连接情况。", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "f0015bac-362", "component": "tidb-tikv", "reason": "Region is unavailable error causing cascading failures across the system", "reasoning_trace": [{"step": 1, "action": "LoadMetrics(tidb-tidb)", "observation": "memory_usage下降63.63%，duration_99th从0.01ms飙升至64.88ms，failed_query_ops异常"}, {"step": 2, "action": "LogSearch(productcatalogservice)", "observation": "Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable错误，failed to query product by id"}, {"step": 3, "action": "TraceAnalysis(f0015bac-362)", "observation": "productcatalogservice响应时间激增至3900万毫秒，Region is unavailable错误传播"}]}, "report_analysis_completed": true}
